text: Eugenana is a rural suburb of Devonport, Tasmania, Australia. Lake Eugenana which is 123 metres above sea level is situated here. There is a caravan park situated by the lake. The Tasmanian Arboretum, 60ha of park, consisting of flora and fauna is at Eugenana. ==External links== *The Tasmanian Arboretum *Lakeside Caravan Park Devonport ==References== Category:Suburbs of Devonport, Tasmania
